Module  : Compatibility: mbstring extension
Version : 1.0.0
Author  : Phorum Dev Team

This module implements a fallback for PHP's mb_substr() function,
in case PHP does not have the "mbstring" extension enabled.

Install:
--------

- Unpack the archive and move the directory "compat_mbstring" to the
  directory "mods" within your Phorum installation (unless this module
  was packaged with your Phorum release);

- Login as administrator in Phorum's administrative interface and
  go to the "Modules" section;

- Enable the module "Compatibility: mbstring extension".


